ement\", \"from\": 1834, \"to\": 1851}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I wanted to free Costanza from the male gaze which has clouded our view for the past 400 years,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1864, \"to\": 1971, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Costanza\", \"from\": 1882, \"to\": 1890}, {\"ngram\": \"the male gaze\", \"from\": 1896, \"to\": 1909}, {\"ngram\": \"our view\", \"from\": 1928, \"to\": 1936}, {\"ngram\": \"the past 400 years\", \"from\": 1941, \"to\": 1959}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Writing [her story] was also a way for me to examine the ways in which male coercion and violence are still used to control women today.\\\"\", \"from\": 1972, \"to\": 2110, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her story\", \"from\": 1982, \"to\": 1991}, {\"ngram\": \"a way\", \"from\": 2002, \"to\": 2007}, {\"ngram\": \"the ways\", \"from\": 2026, \"to\": 2034}, {\"ngram\": \"male coercion\", \"from\": 2044, \"to\": 2057}, {\"ngram\": \"violence\", \"from\": 2062, \"to\": 2070}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 2097, \"to\": 2102}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Digest TheMetropolitan Museum of Artin New York attracted more local visitors last year than it did prior to the Covid-19 pandemic.\", \"from\": 2112, \"to\": 2248, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2112, \"end\": 2122, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Digest_(Roman_law)\", \"score\": 0.9997336706836197, \"rank\": 0.0002664002664003856, \"text\": \"The Digest\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Digest_(Roman_law)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Digest_(Roman_law)\"}, {\"begin\": 2156, \"end\": 2164, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.9999999999363354, \"rank\": 6.363047190414452e-11, \"text\": \"New York\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more local visitors\", \"from\": 2174